title: Refrigerator Humidity Slide Button
description: Refrigerator Humidity Slide Button PartSelect Number PS285537 Manufacturer Part Number WR02X11174 This humidity slide is located on the handle of the vegetable/meat drawer.

installationInstructions.author: chuck from Lake Worth, FL
installationInstructions.title: Slide broke, then the drawer broke due to misuse
installationInstructions.content: I removed the two screws for the broken slide rail, installed the new slide rail in very short order. Put together the drawer pieces and voila... easy repair
